rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 700蚊換過部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊有咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n換mon 1000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有買1088多1年個個保用。長期爆mon 長期都係200"},{"pid":"aabb1f869d1be16521a7967cb72d88613410d697","tid":89870,"uid":52824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:03:46.000Z","msg":"又高登講到連登都有人中伏<br />\n無得好怨啦係咪?<br />\n努力儲錢買新機啦"},{"pid":"b714bb9fcd3d43b985ce6b6659eca818658beada","tid":89870,"uid":6179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:09:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n邊有咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n換mon 1000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有買1088多1年個個保用。長期爆mon 長期都係200</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你估個個肯加apple care咩"},{"pid":"107f92ac4dc40780a7019baa3f046d2ea10a8097","tid":89870,"uid":48633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:15:16.000Z","msg":"LG g5 爆Mon 邊到整好  請各巴打指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca477dedc643c7ad8b08d1ae377e8f000e78dcc","tid":89870,"uid":54066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:13:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>LG g5 爆Mon 邊到整好  請各巴打指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上taobao買mon去華強北睇住佢换"},{"pid":"267a9a5d14700aa024e7702baef97e35f1610a80","tid":89870,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T00:51:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下如果淨換塊玻璃會唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇得淨係換玻璃</blockquote><br />\n<br /